    penny_moment: `Penny checked her pile three mornings in a row. She had not added to it. She had not touched it. But each morning — very slightly — it was bigger than the day before. She turned this over for a long time. Nobody was adding to it. It was just... growing. She cannot stop thinking about how strange that is.`,
