    app_text_1014: `Money left in the right place multiplies over time. The extra it earned last month starts earning too — so the growth is not flat, it accelerates. Your family's portfolio is a live demonstration. The number today is larger than the sum of what went in. That gap is the growth.`,
    app_text_15: `Compounding is the only wealth-creation mechanism that accelerates without additional effort. The longer the runway, the larger the terminal number — non-linearly. Look at your portfolio's return. Now imagine that rate applied to the next 20 years. The maths is not intuitive.`,
